			&none         &mmv MOVE_LEFT  &mmv MOVE_DOWN  &mmv MOVE_RIGHT  &none      &kp C_PP          &kp N2  &kp KP_N4  &kp KP_N5  &kp KP_N6  &kp KP_PLUS      &kp RBKT   
